		    <title outputclass="H3_1_9" xtrf="Grey" class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">570.308</ph> Award.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
			      <ol class="- topic/ol " id="d983e13">
				        <li otherprops="H5_abc"
                audience="GSAR"
                outputclass="Grey_H5_abc"
                xtrf="Grey"
                class="- topic/li ">
					          <p outputclass="H5_abc"
                  xtrf="Grey"
                  class="- topic/p "
                  id="d974e17">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						             Make award to the responsible offeror whose proposal represents the best value after evaluation in accordance with the factors and subfactors in the SFO.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li otherprops="H5_abc"
                audience="GSAR"
                outputclass="Grey_H5_abc"
                xtrf="Grey"
                class="- topic/li ">
					          <p outputclass="H5_abc"
                  xtrf="Grey"
                  class="- topic/p "
                  id="d974e26">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						             Make award in writing and in the timeframe specified in the SFO.</p>
					          <ol class="- topic/ol " id="d983e32">
						            <li otherprops="H6_123"
                      audience="GSAR"
                      outputclass="Grey_H6_123"
                      xtrf="Grey"
                      class="- topic/li ">
							              <p outputclass="H6_123"
                        xtrf="Grey"
                        class="- topic/p "
                        id="d974e36">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 If the contracting officer cannot make an award in that time, request in writing from each offeror an extension of the acceptance period through a specific date.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li otherprops="H6_123"
                      audience="GSAR"
                      outputclass="Grey_H6_123"
                      xtrf="Grey"
                      class="- topic/li ">
							              <p outputclass="H6_123"
                        xtrf="Grey"
                        class="- topic/p "
                        id="d974e45">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 If time is critical, the contracting officer may request the extensions orally. The contracting officer must make a record of the request and confirm it promptly in writing.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li otherprops="H5_abc"
                audience="GSAR"
                outputclass="Grey_H5_abc"
                xtrf="Grey"
                class="- topic/li ">
					          <p outputclass="H5_abc"
                  xtrf="Grey"
                  class="- topic/p "
                  id="d974e56">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						             Notify unsuccessful offerors in writing or electronically in accordance with FAR 15.501 and 15.503(b).</p>
				        </li>
				        <li otherprops="H5_abc"
                audience="GSAR"
                outputclass="Grey_H5_abc"
                xtrf="Grey"
                class="- topic/li ">
					          <p outputclass="H5_abc"
                  xtrf="Grey"
                  class="- topic/p "
                  id="d974e65">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						             The source selection authority may reject all proposals received in response to an SFO, if doing so is in the best interest of the Government.</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
